kobo-restore is (c) 2011 by David Leaman. It is released under the
MIT license and a CC Attribution license; see the LICENSE file for 
details.

The INSTALL file contains instructions to set up this program for use.

Before running kobo-restore, you should:
 1. edit `kobo-restore` and make sure that the paths in the 
    "configuration" section are correct.
 2. make kobo-restore executable by running `chmod 755 kobo-restore`

If you have any questions or comments about this software, visit the
project page at:
    http://code.google.com/p/kobo-restore/
There you will find the source code for the project, as well as ways
to contact the developers. You can also become a developer by joining
the project.

